# Force LF line endings for every text file on every platform.
#
# Windows checkouts with `core.autocrlf=true` would otherwise rewrite LF
# to CRLF in the working tree, which breaks:
#   - knot.ticket/parse (matches the literal "---\n" / "\n---\n" fences)
#   - the checked-in-schema-is-in-sync test (knot.schema.json byte-compare)
# Pinning eol=lf at the gitattributes layer guarantees the working tree
# matches the index on every OS.
* text=auto eol=lf
